Support for the UI related to geodetic coordinate selection and geodetic objects.

Interface Summary

Class Summary

CategoryTree Implements a category tree for use in coordinate system selection
CoordinateSystemSelection A panel used for coordinate system selection.
CoordSysDesignerPanel A panel used to design coordinate systems.

CoordSysTreePanel A panel used for coordinate system selection.

NumericField Implements a numeric field (extends a JTextField)
ProjectionParameterEntryPanel A panel used for projection entry.
TableObjectField Implements selection of a named object within a combo boc
